Reported by @grrrwaaa  in #44 

> Related; found a couple of places where a pedantic compiler wouldn't convert void * to HMODULE:
>
>FreeLibrary(handle);
>to
>FreeLibrary((HMODULE)handle);
>
>return GetProcAddress(handle, name);
>to
>return GetProcAddress((HMODULE)handle, name);

